    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Name": "Goth Kweebec",
      "Line": "Look. I know how this goes.",
      "UiPage": "Classic_Dialogue.ui",
      "UiFragment": "Classic_Dialogue_Fragment.ui"
    },
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Name": "Goth Kweebec",
      "Line": "You showed up to a community full of normal-looking Kweebecs. Of course you gotta find out what's going on with the one overt freak.",
      "UiPage": "Classic_Dialogue.ui",
      "UiFragment": "Classic_Dialogue_Fragment.ui"
    },
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Name": "Goth Kweebec",
      "Line": "And I've already heard it all, you know. \"Oh, she just wants attention.\" \"Oh, she's so scary. Will she clip my shoots in my sleep or something?\"",
      "UiPage": "Classic_Dialogue.ui",
      "UiFragment": "Classic_Dialogue_Fragment.ui"
    }
  ],
  "AdvanceText": "Continue",
  "End": {
    "Type": "Standard",
    "Line": {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "If you have your own commentary to add onto that, please spare me."
    },
    "Name": {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "Goth Kweebec"
    },
    "UiPage": "Classic_Dialogue.ui",
    "UiFragment": "Classic_Dialogue_Fragment.ui",
    "Choices": [
      {
        "Id": "Standard",
        "Text": "You're assuming a lot out of me. I literally just came here to say hi.",
        "Action": {
          "Id": "Advance",
          "Next": "Gk1_2ABCD-3A"
        }
      },
      {
        "Id": "Standard",
        "Text": "Maybe you should consider that those other people are right.",
